solutions.content:
We add `candidates` workers from the left and right to the min heap, with their indexes.

We also track how many candidates we pushed from left (`i`) and right (`j`).

Then, we pull the next workers with the minimum cost. Based on their index, we push another worker from left or right to the heap.

